data.title: Bicycle Crunch
instruction: Lie on your back with your hands behind your head
Lift your shoulders off the ground and bring one elbow towards the opposite knee
Switch sides, mimicking a pedaling motion

data.title: Mountain Climbers
instruction: Start in a push-up position with your hands under your shoulders
Bring one knee towards your chest and quickly switch legs
Keep your core engaged and back straight
Repeat for the desired time or repetitions
